            <bug_when>2014-10-01 17:40:17 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>I just found out that cordova/phonegap has something in their own config.xml to solve the issue:

&lt;preference name=&quot;DisallowOverscroll&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;

If it&#39;s still desired to dove this in JavaScript, a possible (but still a bit hacky) solution can be found here:

https://github.com/luster-io/prevent-overscroll

I would suggest to close this issue with Won&#39;t Fix because the behavior can be easily configured within PhoneGap.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
